data.description: This charming well maintained home is centrally located and is nestled in a cul-de-sac. As soon as you walk in you are greeted with an oversized living room and large picturesque windows! This home boasts many updates within the past three years such as new flooring, paint and fixtures, as well as a new roof in 2022! Ask your realtor for a complete list of updates. Call to get your showing appointment scheduled today!
